  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvb-uy/cdn/cc908ac6fdaf59df26e6be8b96ca028a00860a0c/desc/create-questing/banner.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1123\" height=\"429\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/790272037578473512?label=Discord&amp;color=393939&amp;labelColor=7693ef&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"258\" height=\"33\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<em><a href=\"https://legacy.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/aoc\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/MADE FOR-ALL OF CREATE-393939?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=CurseForge&amp;labelColor=7693ef&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"269\" height=\"33\" /></a>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: 8px;\"><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/elocindev\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ElocinDev-SUPPORT%20ME-393939?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=Ko-Fi&amp;labelColor=7693ef&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"260\" height=\"33\" /></a></span></em></p>\n<p><br /><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvb-uy/cdn/cc908ac6fdaf59df26e6be8b96ca028a00860a0c/desc/create-questing/1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1123\" height=\"827\" /><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvb-uy/cdn/cc908ac6fdaf59df26e6be8b96ca028a00860a0c/desc/create-questing/2.webp\" width=\"1123\" height=\"446\" /><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvb-uy/cdn/cc908ac6fdaf59df26e6be8b96ca028a00860a0c/desc/create-questing/3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1119\" height=\"445\" /></p>\n\n## Create Questing\n\nAdds a create-like blueprint theme to FTB Quests create chapters. It is highly configurable in the create_questing.json config file, you can select multiple chapters, change its colors, size, and more!\n\nIt also adds the Blueprint item which serves the same purpose as a questbook, but is craftable and fits more in a create theme.\n\nThis mod was made for the All of Create modpack, coming soon to Modrinth.",
